40:33.431 --> 40:34.603
OR PRACTICAL.

40:34.603 --> 40:35.764
AND AWFUL.

40:35.764 --> 40:37.145
WELL, YOU WANT
ANOTHER BABY, TOO.

40:37.145 --> 40:39.818
YEAH, BECAUSE I LOVE BABIES.
